*To Test*
1. Create an alloy app
2. Include a js file under {{app/lib}}
3. Add  the js file under {{optimizingExeptions}} of {{config.json}}
{code}
{
  //...
  "optimizingExceptions": [
        "something.js",
    ],
  //...
}
{code}
4. Compile and look into output, under {{----- OPTIMIZING -----}}, you should not see the file being optimized.
